{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-publication-index-js","path":"/dp/120/gaining-from-digital-disruption-the-thai-financial-landscape-in-the-digital-era/","result":{"data":{"meta":{"siteMetadata":{"collections":[{"collection":"abridged","title":"aBRIDGEd","subtitle":"Making Research Accessible","url":"/abridged/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"thaipublica","title":"เศรษฐศาสตร์เข้า \"ท่า\"","subtitle":"Making Research Make Sense","url":"/thaipublica/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"pierspectives","title":"PIERspectives","subtitle":"Making Research Comprehensible","url":"/pierspectives/","placeholder":"pierspectives"},{"collection":"dp","title":"Discussion Paper","subtitle":"Making Research Inaccessible","url":"/dp/","placeholder":"dp"},{"collection":"members","title":"Members","subtitle":"Making Research Possible","url":"/pier-research-network/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"announcements","title":"Announcements","subtitle":"Making Research Public","url":"/announcements/","placeholder":"announcements"},{"collection":"blog","title":"PIER Blog","subtitle":"Making Research Public","url":"/blog/","placeholder":"blog"},{"collection":"conferences","title":"Conferences","subtitle":"Making Research Big","url":"/conferences/","placeholder":"conferences"},{"collection":"workshops","title":"Workshops and Forums","subtitle":"Making Research Work","url":"/workshops/","placeholder":"seminars"},{"collection":"seminars","title":"PIER Economic Seminars","subtitle":"Making Research Better","url":"/seminars/","placeholder":"seminars"},{"collection":"exchange","title":"PIER Research Exchange","subtitle":"Making Research Exchangable","url":"/exchange/","placeholder":"seminars"}],"series":[{"series":"Industry Transformation","placeholder":"industry-transformation"},{"series":"Public Economics","placeholder":"public-economics"}]}},"mdx":{"body":"var _excluded = [\"components\"];\n\nfunction _extends() { _extends = Object.assign || function (target) { for (var i = 1; i < arguments.length; i++) { var source = arguments[i]; for (var key in source) { if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(source, key)) { target[key] = source[key]; } } } return target; }; return _extends.apply(this, arguments); }\n\nfunction _objectWithoutProperties(source, excluded) { if (source == null) return {}; var target = _objectWithoutPropertiesLoose(source, excluded); var key, i; if (Object.getOwnPropertySymbols) { var sourceSymbolKeys = Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(source); for (i = 0; i < sourceSymbolKeys.length; i++) { key = sourceSymbolKeys[i]; if (excluded.indexOf(key) >= 0) continue; if (!Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable.call(source, key)) continue; target[key] = source[key]; } } return target; }\n\nfunction _objectWithoutPropertiesLoose(source, excluded) { if (source == null) return {}; var target = {}; var sourceKeys = Object.keys(source); var key, i; for (i = 0; i < sourceKeys.length; i++) { key = sourceKeys[i]; if (excluded.indexOf(key) >= 0) continue; target[key] = source[key]; } return target; }\n\n/* @jsxRuntime classic */\n\n/* @jsx mdx */\nvar _frontmatter = {\n  \"id\": \"120\",\n  \"title\": \"Gaining from Digital Disruption: the Thai Financial Landscape in the Digital Era\",\n  \"authors\": [\"Thammarak Moenjak\", \"Vorapat Praneeprachachon\", \"Tanatas Bumpenboon\", \"Pornchanok Bumrungruan\", \"Chompoonoot Monchaitrakul\"],\n  \"date\": \"2019-12-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"pdf\": \"pier_dp_120.pdf\"\n};\nvar layoutProps = {\n  _frontmatter: _frontmatter\n};\nvar MDXLayout = \"wrapper\";\nreturn function MDXContent(_ref) {\n  var components = _ref.components,\n      props = _objectWithoutProperties(_ref, _excluded);\n\n  return mdx(MDXLayout, _extends({}, layoutProps, props, {\n    components: components,\n    mdxType: \"MDXLayout\"\n  }), mdx(\"p\", null, \"This paper examines competitiveness of the Thai financial sector through the dimensions of depth, access, efficiency, and stability, as compared to peers. The paper finds that while the Thai financial sector compares reasonably well with peers in most dimensions, it does not fare well in term of SME access to bank credit. Using Panzar-Rosse H-Statistic, the paper also examines competition in the Thai banking sector and finds that the level of competition in the Thai banking sector is consistently high over the sample period. The results raise the question: Why does SME access to bank credit remain low, despite high level of competition in the banking sector? This puzzle is important since SMEs are a key driver of the Thai economy. Reviewing results from various studies and interviews with SMEs and bank credit officers, the paper identifies several bottlenecks in the SME lending process that may lead to market failures. Using data from 1.29 million individual SME loan contracts obtained from 15 Thai commercial banks, and six Specialized Financial Institutions (SFIs), the paper finds that only a few banks attempt to penetrate SMEs at the lower tiers of loan size and income. Although SME lending by SFIs are found to be a good complement to SME lending by banks, the fact remains that fewer than half of SMEs in Thailand have loans from these financial institutions. The paper then discusses how several initiatives have been attempted to harness the power of technology and data to help improve SME access to finance, whether from traditional banks or other types of players. Lessons from the case of SME financing and from other segments of financial sectors in selected countries are then drawn into common themes that might help guide the design of financial landscape in the digital era.\"));\n}\n;\nMDXContent.isMDXComponent = true;","fields":{"slug":"/dp/120/gaining-from-digital-disruption-the-thai-financial-landscape-in-the-digital-era/","collection":"dp","shorturl":"/dp/120/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gaining from Digital Disruption: the Thai Financial Landscape in the Digital Era","subtitle":null,"series":null,"authors":["Thammarak Moenjak","Vorapat Praneeprachachon","Tanatas Bumpenboon","Pornchanok Bumrungruan","Chompoonoot Monchaitrakul"],"date":"2019-12-24T00:00:00.000Z","updated":null,"cover":null,"excerpt":null,"bibliography":null,"topics":null,"tags":null,"layout":null,"pdf":{"publicURL":"/static/b68c133afd41f8fc863bbc51628c5ace/pier_dp_120.pdf"}},"authors":[{"frontmatter":{"memberid":"Chompoonoot Monchaitrakul","title":"Chompoonoot Monchaitrakul","org":"bot","email":"ChompooM@bot.or.th","image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/dd515/profile.jpg","srcSet":"/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/6ac16/profile.jpg 50w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/e07e1/profile.jpg 100w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/dd515/profile.jpg 200w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/47930/profile.jpg 400w","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/dbc4a/profile.webp 50w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/d8057/profile.webp 100w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/2e34e/profile.webp 200w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/416c3/profile.webp 400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"}]},"width":200,"height":200}}},"exclude":null},"fields":{"slug":"/en/members/chompoonoot-monchaitrakul/","lang":"en"}},{"frontmatter":{"memberid":"Chompoonoot Monchaitrakul","title":"ชมพูนุท มนต์ชัยตระกูล","org":"bot","email":"ChompooM@bot.or.th","image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/dd515/profile.jpg","srcSet":"/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/6ac16/profile.jpg 50w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/e07e1/profile.jpg 100w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/dd515/profile.jpg 200w,\n/static/386b3889cf888cd713ab21696e079b3d/47930/